18
00:03:42.724 --> 00:03:44.726
Yes. I should! Help me dress.

19
00:03:47.604 --> 00:03:49.564
Ooh...

20
00:03:53.735 --> 00:03:54.945
Ooh...

21
00:04:02.244 --> 00:04:03.453
Princess...

22
00:04:04.996 --> 00:04:06.331
your dress?

23
00:04:39.698 --> 00:04:41.450
Princess?

24
00:04:41.533 --> 00:04:43.743
- It's coming.
- The afterbirth!

25
00:04:54.171 --> 00:04:56.381
A boy. I've just heard.

26
00:04:56.465 --> 00:04:58.091
- Yes.
- Well done.

27
00:04:59.468 --> 00:05:02.429
- Where are you going?
- She wants to see him.

28
